Coaching vacancies • Bexley is seeking a boys middle school tennis coach. Resumes should be submitted to athletic director Corinne Taylor at Corinne.Taylor@bexleyschools.org.
College signings • Brad Davis and Carly Davis of Dublin Jerome have committed to run cross country and track at Miami University.
Miscellaneous • The Mid-State League is seeking a soccer official assignor. Resumes should be directed to commissioner Jim Hayes at mslcomm@live.com by Nov. 15.
